        <oboInOwl:creation_date>2013-10-12T17:21:09Z</oboInOwl:creation_date>
        <oboInOwl:inSubset>envoPolar</oboInOwl:inSubset>
        <rdfs:comment>Unlike biomes, ecoregions are geographically defined entities. ENVO&apos;s sister project, GAZ, contains terms for instances of ecoregions (e.g. Beringia lowland tundra). Requests for new terms should be directed to GAZ. ENVO will only contain this top-level class. The class&apos; definition is preliminary and will be aligned to BFO.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>ecoregion</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
