        <owl:annotatedTarget>Snow is an environmental material which is primarily composed of flakes of crystalline water ice.</owl:annotatedTarget>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/7769</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
