        <oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>congelation process</oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>
        <rdfs:comment>Sometimes the increase in viscosity is great enough to crystallize or solidify the substance in question.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">material congelation process</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
