        <oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>frozen ground</oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>
        <rdfs:comment>Perennially and seasonally frozen ground can vary from being partially to extensively frozen depending on the extent of the phase change. It may be described as hard frozen ground, plastic frozen ground, or dry frozen ground, depending on the pore ice and unfrozen water contents and its compressibility under load.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">frozen land</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
