        <obo:IAO_0000115>A pathologic primary tumor stage for ovary according to AJCC 7th edition indicating that the tumor is limited to one ovary; capsule intact, no tumor on ovarian surface and no malignant cells in ascites or peritoneal washings.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000117>Chris Stoeckert, Helena Ellis</obo:IAO_0000117>
