        <obo:IAO_0000114 rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000120"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A clinical tumor stage group according to AJCC 7th edition indicating a carcinoma in situ (or melanoma in situ for melanoma of the skin or germ cell neoplasia in situ for testicular germ cell tumors) and generally is considered to have no metastatic potential.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A clinical tumor stage group according to AJCC 7th edition indicating a carcinoma in situ (or melanoma in situ for melanoma of the skin or germ cell neoplasia in situ for testicular germ cell tumors) and generally is considered to have no metastatic potential. </obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000117>Chris Stoeckert, Helena Ellis</obo:IAO_0000117>
        <obo:IAO_0000118>Stage 0</obo:IAO_0000118>
        <obo:IAO_0000119>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer_staging</obo:IAO_0000119>
        <obo:IAO_0000234>NCI BBRB</obo:IAO_0000234>
        <rdfs:label>Stage 0 (AJCC 7th)</rdfs:label>
